details.name: Freezing Field
details.description: CHANNELED - Surrounds Crystal Maiden with random icy explosions that slow enemies and deal massive damage. Grants bonus armor while channeling. Lasts 10 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Applies Frostbite to any unit that has been standing in the Freezing Field for over 2.5 seconds.
